3. Business License Requirement & Pricing

- Teams with more than 25 users must obtain a paid business license.
- Pricing (per active user, billed monthly) is as follows:
  - Users 26–250: $2.90 per user per month
  - Users 251–1'000: $2.65 per user per month
  - Users 1'001–10'000: $2.25 per user per month
  - Users above 10'000: $1.90 per user per month
- To obtain a business license or for commercial inquiries, contact the copyright
  holder for a formal agreement.

